alert the enemy.

339
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,959
Take care.

340
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,000
Sure.

341
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:23,680
Hello.

342
00:21:23,719 --> 00:21:24,400
Hello.

343
00:21:24,439 --> 00:21:26,520
I really appreciate
reporter Li's talent.

344
00:21:26,599 --> 00:21:28,359
