358
00:21:58,939 --> 00:22:00,780
(Insurance agencies won't sell stocks
in large amount by the end of the year)

359
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,280
This is our newspaper.

360
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:04,479
This report was written by Li Lu, right?

361
00:22:04,599 --> 00:22:06,400
Yes, what's wrong?

362
00:22:06,479 --> 00:22:07,839
You are so experienced in media.

363
00:22:08,319 --> 00:22:10,839
Please look at this report of Yutian.

364
00:22:11,040 --> 00:22:13,520
