367
00:22:19,199 --> 00:22:20,800
Well, you're an outsider.

368
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:23,199
If everything our reporters reported

369
00:22:23,439 --> 00:22:24,959
was after it has been made public,

370
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:26,920
