372
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:31,040
Yes.

373
00:22:31,599 --> 00:22:33,520
But you may not find him.

374
00:22:34,119 --> 00:22:35,000
Why?

375
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:37,599
