377
00:22:39,959 --> 00:22:41,640
Who knows where he's moving to now?

378
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:43,680
From Guizhou.

379
00:22:45,239 --> 00:22:46,920
So you have the address on his ID?

380
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:57,359
Excuse me, do you have anyone

381
00:22:57,439 --> 00:22:58,560
named Li Lu here?

382
00:22:59,119 --> 00:23:01,000
Li Lu resigned a year ago.

383
00:23:01,079 --> 00:23:02,239
He also moved.

384
00:23:02,479 --> 00:23:03,599
No one knows where he is now.

385
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,640
One year ago.

386
00:23:05,719 --> 00:23:08,000
That means he resigned
as soon as the report was published.

387
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:11,000
Yes, that means
he's afraid of being found out.

388
00:23:11,239 --> 00:23:12,640
He was pretty sure

389
00:23:12,719 --> 00:23:14,000
