who gave you the information?

393
00:23:23,719 --> 00:23:25,680
What happened?

394
00:23:26,119 --> 00:23:27,160
It is my fault.

395
00:23:27,560 --> 00:23:29,000
I didn't expect it so complicated.

396
00:23:29,560 --> 00:23:30,640
Our investigation must have threatened

397
00:23:30,719 --> 00:23:31,839
the interests of the opponent.

398
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,239
So...

399
00:23:33,479 --> 00:23:36,000
They are putting all their eggs
in one basket.

400
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:39,640
Lin Xiangyuan is so cruel and merciless.

401
00:23:40,119 --> 00:23:41,760
Maybe it is not Lin Xiangyuan.

402
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:45,400
He certainly didn't want me
to go back to Yutian.

403
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:49,000
But he should not be that kind of crazy.

404
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:51,479
Oh,

405
00:23:54,119 --> 00:23:55,160
have a look at

406
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:02,040
these investment accounts.

407
00:24:02,119 --> 00:24:03,239
I have investigated.

408
00:24:03,719 --> 00:24:06,000
Before Li Lu reported it,

409
00:24:06,079 --> 00:24:08,319
that is when Yutian and
S.G signed the contract,

410
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,760
all these accounts

411
00:24:09,839 --> 00:24:12,000
kept buying large
amount of Yutian's stock.

412
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,160
When did they sell the stock?

413
00:24:14,239 --> 00:24:15,560
That's so weird.

414
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:17,479
They didn't sell.

415
00:24:17,839 --> 00:24:19,400
It is a large amount of money.

416
00:24:20,199 --> 00:24:21,520
Even with profits, they did not sell.

417
00:24:23,439 --> 00:24:24,640
What were they thinking of?

418
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,920
They didn't care about the profits.

419
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:28,719
Siyang,

420
00:24:28,800 --> 00:24:29,880
use all your resources,

421
00:24:30,520 --> 00:24:31,920
and help me investigate
all these accounts'

422
00:24:31,959 --> 00:24:33,160
sources.

423
00:24:33,239 --> 00:24:34,800
I will call Shangguan,

424
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,640
and ask him to help find Li Lu.

425
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:39,119
You focus on
investigating these accounts.

426
00:24:40,319 --> 00:24:42,680
Mr. Lin,
according to our market research,

427
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:43,959
