431
00:24:48,199 --> 00:24:49,640
We want to initial a plan.

432
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,520
So, we hope, next year,

433
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,560
with the financial budget,

434
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:55,040
