435
00:24:55,319 --> 00:24:57,319
Hope Mr. Lin will consider it.

436
00:25:00,079 --> 00:25:00,920
Hello.

437
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,040
Mr. Lin?

438
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:07,839
Hello.

439
00:25:09,439 --> 00:25:10,520
Here you are.

440
00:25:12,719 --> 00:25:14,119
