441
00:25:14,959 --> 00:25:17,599
Thank you for meeting me in person.

442
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:17,640
Thank you for meeting me in person.

443
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:23,839
OK. You go back to your work
and close the door for me.

