00:25:30,079 --> 00:25:32,640
Mr. Yu, I overheard a piece of news.

445
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:34,839
To be precise,

446
00:25:35,359 --> 00:25:37,359
Yutian will cooperate with
an oversea company, S.G.

447
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,560
