462
00:26:17,119 --> 00:26:19,079
I'm working for Yutian.

463
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:21,319
We have considered that.

464
00:26:21,599 --> 00:26:23,160
If the acquisition is successful,

465
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:26,040
we will continue to employ you

466
00:26:26,199 --> 00:26:28,000
