483
00:27:05,599 --> 00:27:07,359
You should be very clear.

484
00:27:07,479 --> 00:27:08,359
Now, I tell you.

485
00:27:08,439 --> 00:27:11,040
In a few days, we will formally
submit to the CSRC

486
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,920
